erlman | accessdate = 2014-10-26 | date = 2008-12-17 | agency = Associated Press | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201145234/http://www.today.com/id/28282312 | work = TODAY.com | publisher = NBCNEWS.com | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[全国公共广播电台|全国公共广播电台]]形容这场四重奏演出“以美丽和宁静感动了许多人”，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》称其为“（如）双唇般同步与和谐的古典音乐”<ref>{{cite web | title = Yo-Yo Ma on Recorded Music at Inauguration: What's The Big Deal With Inauguration 'Lip-Synching'? | accessdate = 2014-10-26 | date = 2009-01-23 | publisher = National Public Radio | author = Grundmann, Anya | url = http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=99816993 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140327093359/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=99816993 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-03-27 }}</ref>。[[艾瑞莎·弗蘭克林|艾瑞莎·弗蘭克林]]戴着一顶镶满[[施华洛世奇|施华洛世奇]]水晶蝴蝶结的帽子<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1603107/20090120/franklin_aretha.jhtml | title = Aretha Franklin's Performance at Barack Obama's Inauguration: A Milestone in a Historic Career: Soul singer, who performed 'My Country 'Tis of Thee,' also sang at Martin Luther King's funeral. | accessdate = 2014-10-26 | date = 2009-01-20 | author = Wiederhorn, Jon | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140703053744/http://www.mtv.com/news/1603107/aretha-franklins-performance-at-barack-obamas-inauguration-a-milestone-in-a-historic-career/ | archivedate = 2014-07-03 | publisher = MTV Networks | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/alltherage/2009/01/inaugural-hat-t.html | title = All The Rage: The Image Staff Muses On The Culture Of Keeping Up Appearances In Hollywood And Beyond | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130901072746/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/alltherage/2009/01/inaugural-hat-t.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-10-26 | date = 2009-01-20 | author = Wiederhorn, Jon | work = Los Angeles Times | archivedate = 2013-09-01 }}</ref>。

