e="LIb">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116203846/http://blogs.sun-sentinel.com/tv/2009/01/the-burning-question-of-inauguration-morning-was-would-the-superlatives-run-out-before-the-day-does---before-the-sun-came-u.html |deadurl=yes |url=http://blogs.sun-sentinel.com/tv/2009/01/the-burning-question-of-inauguration-morning-was-would-the-superlatives-run-out-before-the-day-does---before-the-sun-came-u.html |title=Live Inauguration blog |accessdate=2014-10-26 |date=2009-01-20 |work=Sun Sentinel |location=Broward County, FL |author=Jicha, Tom |archivedate=2014-01-16 }}</ref><ref name="LB">{{cite news | url = http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/01/20/live-blog-the-inauguration-of-barack-obama/ | title = Live Blog: The Inauguration of Barack Obama | accessdate = 2014-10-26 | date = 2009-01-20 | work = The New York Times | author = Seelye, Katharine | publisher = The New York Times Company | archivedate = 2014-10-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141026143212/http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/01/20/live-blog-the-inauguration-of-barack-obama/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过根据[[美利坚合众国宪法第二十条修正案|联邦宪法第二十条修正案]]，前任总统布什的任期在2009年1月20日中午12点期满，奥巴马也正是从这一刻起正式成为美国总统。现场响起[[21响礼炮|21响礼炮]]，向新总统致敬，军乐队演奏《[[向统帅致敬|向统帅致敬]]》和《鼓号齐鸣》<ref name="honors" /><ref>{{cite news | title = The 56th Presidential Inauguration | accessdate = 2014-10-26 | date = 2009-01 | work = The Washington Post | url = http://voices.washingtonpost.com/inauguration-watch/Inaugural%20Media%20Guide.pdf | publisher = The Washington Post Company | archive-date = 2012-10-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121005174918/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/inauguration-watch/Inaugural%20Media%20Guide.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

