就职游行从美国国会大厦开始沿[[宾夕法尼亚大道|宾夕法尼亚大道]]至白宫北翼为止。出于安全方面的考量，奥巴马夫妇在游行期间的大部分时间里都坐在[[美国总统座车|总统座车]]上<ref name="parade">{{cite news |url=http://www.news.com.au/dailytelegraph/story/0,22049,24942113-5015669,00.html |title=In a New Tux, Obama Seeks the Proper Tone |accessdate=2009-01-24 |date=2009-01-21 |publisher=The Daily Telegraph (Australia) |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206171912/http://www.news.com.au/dailytelegraph/story/0%2C22049%2C24942113-5015669%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-02-06 }}</ref>。两人中途两次走出轿车，在宾夕法尼亚大道上步行了一段时间<ref>{{cite news | last = Lawrence | first = J. | date = 2009-01-20 | title = An inaugural parade they won't soon forget | publisher = USAToday}}</ref>。拜登夫妇与他们的孩子[[博·拜登|博]]、亨特（{{lang|en|Hunter}}）和阿什利（{{lang|en|Ashley}}）也多次参与到游行之中<ref>{{cite news | url = http://infoweb.newsbank.com/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_action=doc&p_topdoc=1&p_docnum=1&p_sort=YMD_date:D&p_product=NewsBank&p_text_direct-0=document_id=(%20125E199E22E82C28%20)&p_docid=125E199E22E82C28&p_theme=aggregated5&p_queryname=125E199E22E82C28&f_openurl=yes&p_nbid=T5FL5CQWMTI0MTc5MTM2My4xNzE0MTI6MToxMDoxMjguMTIuMC4w&&p_multi=NWJB | title = Capping a long career, Biden 's swearing-in a climactic moment for Del.'s leading man | accessdate = 2009-04-12 | date = 2009-01-21 | work = The News Journal | location = Wilmington, DE | author = Gaudiano, Nicole}}</ref>。

