81E39F93AA35751C1A96E9C8B63 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

副总统拜登邀请了[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]的多个团体参加游行。特拉华州的游行团体由[[特拉华州志愿消防员协会|特拉华州志愿消防员协会]]领头，拜登是该协会的名誉会员，然后是来自拜登母校[[特拉华大学|特拉华大学]]的“战斗蓝母鸡游行乐队、特拉华州的自豪”（{{lang|en|Fightin' Blue Hen Marching Band, The Pride of Delaware}}）<ref name="parades">{{cite news | title = Inauguration Parade 2009 – Overview and List of Participants: The 56th Inaugural Parade | last = Roche | first = Jennifer | year = 2009 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140712184714/http://chicago.about.com/od/parades/a/InauguralParade.htm | deadurl = yes | publisher = About.com | accessdate = 2014-10-28 | url = http://chicago.about.com/od/parades/a/InauguralParade.htm | archivedate = 2014-07-12 }}</ref>，以及[[特拉华州立大学|特拉华州立大学]]黄蜂逼近暴风雨游行乐队<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121105183638/http://archives.desu.edu/advancement/pr/press_release.php?article_id=479 | url = http://archives.desu.edu/advancement/pr/press_release.php?article_id=479 | title = DSU Band to Perform Jan. 18 Pre-Inaugural Concert | date = 2009-01-07 | publisher = Delaware State University | accessdate = 2012-11-05 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-11-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Black Colleges Well Represented at Inaugural Parade | accessdate = 2014-10-28 | date = 2009-01-21 | work = U.S. News & World Report | archivedate = 2013-06-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130618010812/http://www.usnews.com/education/blogs/paper-trail/2009/01/21/black-colleges-well-represented-at-inaugural-parade | author = Alison Go | url = http://www.usnews.com/education/blogs/paper-trail/2009/01/21/black-colleges-well-represented-at-inaugural-parade }}</ref>。

