==== 就职舞会 ====
总统贝拉克·奥巴马和第一夫人米歇尔·奥巴马出席了2009年1月20日晚的10场官方就职舞会<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ctvnews.ca/obamas-to-twirl-through-10-inaugural-balls-jan-20-1.354613 | title = Obamas to twirl through 10 inaugural balls January 20 | accessdate = 2014-10-28 | date = 2008-12-24 | publisher = CTV Television Network (Canada) | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021224638/http://www.ctvnews.ca/obamas-to-twirl-through-10-inaugural-balls-jan-20-1.354613 }}</ref><ref name="自动生成1">{{cite news | first =  | last =  | title = Complete list of Obama's 10 official inaugural balls | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/washington/2009/01/obama-inaugur-1.html | publisher = The Los Angeles Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121217064730/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/washington/2009/01/obama-inaugur-1.html | date = 2009-01-08 | archivedate = 2012-12-17 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-10-28 }}</ref>。贝拉克身穿的新[[黑色领结|燕尾服]]是由[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]男装企业[[哈特马克斯|哈特·夏弗纳·马克斯]]（{{lang|en|Hart Schaffner Marx}}）制作<ref name="IaNTOStPT" />。他带的领结不是传统的黑色，而是白色。传统主义者认为这在时尚角度有些失礼，因为[[白领结|白色领结]]通常只能搭配白色坎肩<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-09-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130903215927/http://www.luxist.com/2009/01/21/obamas-first-fashion-faux-pas/ | url = http://www.luxist.com/2009/01/21/obamas-first-fashion-faux-pas/ | title = Obama's First Fashion Faux Pas | accessdate = 2013-09-03 | date = 2009-01-29 | work = Luxist | author = Stern, Jared Paul }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141028135036/http://tmagazine.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/01/23/inauguration-michelle-obamas-landslide/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=0 | archivedate = 2014-10-28 | publisher = The New York Time Company | url = http://tmagazine.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/01/23/inauguration-michelle-obamas-landslide/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=0 | title = Inauguration – Michelle Obama's Landslide | accessdate = 2012-10-07 | date = 2009-01-23 | work = The New York Times | author = Stein, Joshua David | dead-url = no }}</ref>。米歇尔·奥巴马身穿白色单肩无袖礼服，由26岁的[[曼哈顿|纽约]]设计师[[吴季刚|吴季刚]]设计，与之相比，两位前第一夫人劳拉·布什和[[希拉里·罗德姆·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]展现的都是自己故乡设计师的作品<ref>{{cite news | first = Robin | last = Givhan | title = All hail the leader of the fashionable world | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/story/2009/01/20/ST2009012004580.html | work = The Washington Post | date = 2009-01-21 | accessdate = 2014-10-28 | publisher = The Washington Post Company | archive-date = 2020-05-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200518032833/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/story/2009/01/20/ST2009012004580.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

总统夫妇这晚的第一站是在[[沃尔特·E·华盛顿会议中心|沃尔特·E·华盛顿会议中心]]举行的“邻里就职舞会”，这里当晚一会举行了6场舞会。奥巴马夫妇随第一首歌，[[碧昂丝·诺利斯|碧昂丝·诺利斯]]翻唱[[伊特·珍|伊特·珍]]的经典歌曲《{{lang|en|[[At_Last|At Last]]}}》（意为《终于》）起舞<ref>{{cite news | title = Obamas dance, celebrate at inaugural balls | work = CNNPolitics.com | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100413151351/http://edition.cnn.com/2009/POLITICS/01/20/inauguration.balls/ | archivedate = 2010-04-13 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2009/POLITICS/01/20/inauguration.balls/ | publisher = Cable News Network | date = 2009-01-21 | accessdate = 2014-10-28 }}</ref>。据总统就职委员会所称，邻里就职舞会是美国历史上第一场提供免费或价格低廉门票的总统就职舞会，与之相比，近年来的多次“就职舞会通常都与美国普通百姓无缘，成了达官贵人和捐助人士的专属圈子”<ref>{{cite news | first = Leaman | last = Amy | title = Obama to Host Virtual Ball | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130530091809/http://www.washingtonian.com/blogs/capitalcomment/inauguration-2009/obama-to-host-virtual-ball.php | work = Washingtonian Magazine | date = 2009-01-05 | accessdate = 2014-10-28 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-05-30 | url = http://www.washingtonian.com/blogs/capitalcomment/inauguration-2009/obama-to-host-virtual-ball.php }}</ref>。还有一部分舞会门票是专为哥伦比亚特区的居民保留<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2012-03-08 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120308083654/http://www.ajc.com/travel/content/travel/otherdestinations/us_stories/2009/01/05/obama_neighborhood_ball.html | title = Obama adds 'Neighborhood Ball' for D.C. Residents | date = 2009-01-05 | work = Atlanta Journal-Constitution | accessdate = 2012-03-08 | url = http://www.ajc.com/travel/content/travel/otherdestinations/us_stories/2009/01/05/obama_neighborhood_ball.html }}</ref>。

