 = Katharine Q. | last = Seelye | title = Obama Invites Flight 1549 Pilot and Crew to Inauguration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141029074002/http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/01/19/obama-invites-flight-1549-pilot-and-crew-to-inauguration/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=0 | publisher = The New York Time Company | deadurl = no | url = http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/01/19/obama-invites-flight-1549-pilot-and-crew-to-inauguration/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=0 | work = The New York Times | date = 2009-01-19 | accessdate = 2014-10-29 | archivedate = 2014-10-29 }}</ref>。

