08/06/06/us-usa-politics-kenya-idUSL0651198320080606 | title = Kenyan group vows to defend Obama from smears | date = 2008-06-06 | publisher = [[路透社|Reuters]] | accessdate = 2014-10-29 | archivedate = 2013-12-13 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。特拉华州总检察长、[[特拉华州国民警民队|特拉华州国民警民队]]军法官、乔·拜登正在[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克]]服役的儿子[[博·拜登|博·拜登]]获得特别休假前来参加典礼活动<ref>{{cite news | url = http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2009/01/16/bidens-son-leaves-iraq-for-inauguration/ | title = Biden's son back from Iraq for the inauguration | accessdate = 2014-10-29 | date = 2009-01-15 | publisher = Cable News Network | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131213014022/http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2009/01/16/bidens-son-leaves-iraq-for-inauguration/ | archivedate = 2013-12-13 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

